{
  "title": "Coverage Collision:",
  "body": "<html><body><div id=\"block-ti-west-content\">\n<article>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--type--text--bleed paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><div class=\"hero__container hero__container--small hero__container--no-image\" data-hero-container=\"\"><div class=\"container container--max-width\"><div class=\"hero__text-container hero__text-container--center hero__text-container__small\"><h1 class=\"u-font-family-secondary hero__title\">Coverage Collision: <br/>Avoiding Gaps Between Crime and Cyber Policies</h1></div></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><p>Commercial crime and cyber liability coverages often overlap, but their distinctions can determine whether a claim is covered or denied. Examine how the two coverages align and where they conflict, with examples ranging from social engineering fraud to AI-enabled threats. Learn to spot exclusions such as voluntary parting, evaluate real claims with ambiguous outcomes, and understand how endorsements and regulatory trends are reshaping coverage. Leave with practical tools to assess exposures and guide clients more confidently. </p><table style=\"font-size:inherit;margin:32px 0;width:100%;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding-right:40px;vertical-align:top;\"><strong>Pricing</strong><br/>$64.00*</td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><strong>Webinar Duration</strong><br/>120 minutes</td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><strong>CE Requirements</strong><br/><a href=\"https://web.theinstitutes.org/ceu/state-requirements\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Verify your state and license CE requirements</a></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><section class=\"star-bar__container u-margin-top container--max-width\"><div class=\"alert-message u-padding-hug-left u-bg-accent-lavender u-font-family-primary\"><span class=\"u-margin-right u-bg-alert-blue\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"u-color-white\" height=\"24\" role=\"presentation\" width=\"24\"><use xlink:href=\"#star\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"></use></svg></span><p>*Enjoy Every Webinar Free with CEU Unlimited  —  <a href=\"#unlimited\">See Below</a> to learn more.<br/>No discount code or pre-paid agreement needed. No hidden or state reporting fees.</p></div></section></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div> <div class=\"paragraph paragraph--type--highlight-bar paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div class=\"u-margin-top u-margin-lg-bottom highlight-bar__container highlight-bar__container--navy\">\n<div class=\"container--max-width\">\n<div class=\"container__grid container__grid--centered container__grid--max-md\">\n<div class=\"highlight-bar__inner\">\n<div class=\"highlight-bar__msg u-text-center\">\n<h2>Webinar Details</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><div class=\"webinar-content\"><h4>Coverage Collision: Avoiding Gaps Between Crime and Cyber Policies</h4><p>Fraud is evolving faster than policies. Learn how crime and cyber coverages collide, where exclusions create risk, and what tomorrow’s threats mean for today’s protections. </p><h4>Topics</h4><ul><li>Differentiate crime coverage from cyber coverage and identify gray areas</li><li>Analyze real claims involving fraud, spoofing, and remote work risks</li><li>Evaluate exclusions and endorsements that impact coverage outcomes</li><li>Recognize new threats such as AI-driven scams and ESG fraud</li><li>Anticipate regulatory shifts and future coverage developments </li></ul></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><div style=\"margin:0 auto;max-width:1200px;text-align:center;\"><h3 style=\"margin-bottom:15px;\">Choose Your Date and Time</h3><div id=\"webinar-buttons\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;justify-content:center;\"><a class=\"btn btn--primary\" data-date=\"2026-01-22\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/coverage-collision-avoiding-gaps-between-crime-and-cyber-policies-20260122\" style=\"flex:1 1 calc(33.333% - 16px);max-width:360px;min-width:260px;text-align:center;\">Thu, January 22 – 1:00 PM EST</a>     <a class=\"btn btn--primary\" data-date=\"2026-02-10\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/coverage-collision-avoiding-gaps-between-crime-and-cyber-policies-20260210\" style=\"flex:1 1 calc(33.333% - 16px);max-width:360px;min-width:260px;text-align:center;\">Tue, February 10 – 1:00 PM EST</a> <a class=\"btn btn--primary\" data-date=\"2026-03-04\" href=\"/ceu/webinars/coverage-collision-avoiding-gaps-between-crime-and-cyber-policies-20260304\" style=\"flex:1 1 calc(33.333% - 16px);max-width:360px;min-width:260px;text-align:center;\">Wed, March 04 – 1:00 PM EST</a> </div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><section id=\"unlimited\"><hr/></section></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<section>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<article class=\"container__grid media-block__container media-block__container--reversed\">\n<div class=\"media-block__img-container\">\n<img alt=\"A pink piggy bank swims cutely in a bath of gold coins. \" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned/public/2023-05/Pig_In_Gold.jpg?itok=bMmCvybb\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned/public/2023-05/Pig_In_Gold.jpg?itok=bMmCvybb 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned_2x/public/2023-05/Pig_In_Gold.jpg?itok=wzo3tkhj  2x\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"media-block__header\">\n<h2 class=\"u-margin-hug\">\n            Enjoy unlimited access to webinars with CEU Unlimited.\n          </h2>\n<hr aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"hr hr--offset hr--md hr--md--offset hr--light\" role=\"presentation\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"media-block__content\">\n<p>As a new or current CEU Unlimited Subscriber, enjoy 12 months of full access to every CEU Webinar. That is in addition to 12 months unlimited access to our robust library of on-demand courses.</p><p>PLUS, there are NO state reporting and NO hidden fees for our webinars and on-demand courses – <strong>the price you see is the price you pay, period.</strong></p><p>Get your CEU Unlimited today.</p><p><em>*CEU Unlimited subscriber webinar discount will be reflected in the checkout process.</em><br/><em><span style=\"color:#A31E2C;\"><strong>No discount code or pre-paid agreement number required!</strong></span></em></p>\n<div class=\"card__btn-container card__btn-container--single\" data-item-id=\"31943\" data-learn-more-external=\"\" data-learn-more-text=\"\" data-learn-more-url=\"\" data-price=\"85.00\" data-product=\"CEU Unlimited Access Program\" data-react-component-id=\"add-to-cart\">\n<button class=\"btn btn--primary btn--disabled\">Add to Cart - &amp;dollar;</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</article>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div></body></html>",
